{"files":{},"source":"https:\/\/excalidraw.com","type":"excalidraw","elements":[{"seed":244351556,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"IsL48FUhtVcBDMt2JV0Gm","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":36,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772607039508,"locked":false,"text":"URL Shortner","version":50,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"a0","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"URL Shortner","height":45,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":743633092,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":8,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-353.65350918606578,"angle":0,"y":-708.73045005594236,"width":237.60002136230469},{"seed":290429380,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"itFONWYPGX3v65AIy6hXb","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772607039508,"locked":false,"text":"1. Functional Requirements\n\n    * Create “Unique” short URL for given long URL.\n    * Redirect short URL -> long URL\n    * Expire after default or specified duration.\n\n    ** Custom aliases\n    ** Analytics\n    ** Admin features (blacklist, whitelist, ratelimit)\n\n2. Non Functional Requirements\n\n    * Low Latency\n        ** Redirects (<=20ms)\n        ** short url creation (<=500ms)\n    * Highly Scalable - (supports millions of read and write requests)\n    * Highly Available (Minimal downtime)\n    * Durable (persitent storage of short->long mapping (no data loss))\n    * Unique alias creation\n \n---\n\n3. Estimations\n\n* Daily redirects 10M (10,000,000)\n* Daily short URL creations 1M (1,000,000)\n* Read:Write ratio 10:1 (read heavy)\n* Peak factor = 10x\n\n\nAverate QPS (Reads)\n\n* Reads: 10,000,000 \/ (24*60*60) = 10,000,000\/86,400 =115.741 QPS ~ 120 QPS\n* Writes -> 1,000,000 \/ (24*60*60) = 1,000,000\/86,400 =11.5741 QPS ~ 12.0 QPS\n\n* Combined = 130 QPS\n\nPeak -> 1.3K QPS\n\n\nStorage\n\n\n4. API Design\n\n* POST \/api\/v1\/shorten\n  request body: { url, userId, expiry }\n  response : 201 { slug, shortUrl, targetUrl, createdAt }\n\n* GET \/{slug}\n  HTTP 301 location header -> target_url\n\n\n\n5. High Level Design \n\n    \n\n","version":1288,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"a1","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. Functional Requirements\n\n    * Create “Unique” short URL for given long URL.\n    * Redirect short URL -> long URL\n    * Expire after default or specified duration.\n\n    ** Custom aliases\n    ** Analytics\n    ** Admin features (blacklist, whitelist, ratelimit)\n\n2. Non Functional Requirements\n\n    * Low Latency\n        ** Redirects (<=20ms)\n        ** short url creation (<=500ms)\n    * Highly Scalable - (supports millions of read and write requests)\n    * Highly Available (Minimal downtime)\n    * Durable (persitent storage of short->long mapping (no data loss))\n    * Unique alias creation\n \n---\n\n3. Estimations\n\n* Daily redirects 10M (10,000,000)\n* Daily short URL creations 1M (1,000,000)\n* Read:Write ratio 10:1 (read heavy)\n* Peak factor = 10x\n\n\nAverate QPS (Reads)\n\n* Reads: 10,000,000 \/ (24*60*60) = 10,000,000\/86,400 =115.741 QPS ~ 120 QPS\n* Writes -> 1,000,000 \/ (24*60*60) = 1,000,000\/86,400 =11.5741 QPS ~ 12.0 QPS\n\n* Combined = 130 QPS\n\nPeak -> 1.3K QPS\n\n\nStorage\n\n\n4. API Design\n\n* POST \/api\/v1\/shorten\n  request body: { url, userId, expiry }\n  response : 201 { slug, shortUrl, targetUrl, createdAt }\n\n* GET \/{slug}\n  HTTP 301 location header -> target_url\n\n\n\n5. High Level Design \n\n    \n\n","height":1475,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":723807612,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":8,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-492.65350918606578,"angle":0,"y":-587.10424060508763,"width":847},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","link":null,"roughness"